@startuml C4_Component_Index_Compatibility
title Component Diagram: Index Compatibility Endpoint

skinparam backgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #64748B
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  FontColor #0F172A
}

rectangle "Client / Tool\nmay call PUT /collections/:collection/index" as client
rectangle "Collections Router\naccepts index request" as router
rectangle "CollectionService.putCollectionIndex\nchecks collection metadata" as service
rectangle "Response\n{ operation_id: 0, status: \"completed\" }" as response

client --> router : Qdrant compatibility call
router --> service : no-op compatibility path
service --> response : acknowledged

note bottom of service
  Current runtime does not build or schedule vector indexes.
  Search is driven by the global one-table layout and exact top-k over embedding.
end note
@enduml
